ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yep. It's nice for international students.

definitely. it provides a perfect place to give a presentation in front of many people and a place where somebody can tell me my mistake in pronunciation. it's totally necessary for a international student.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It helps me to improve my presentation skills. It's useful in my dissertation. And this course helps me to know more about American culture.
this course helps me raise my confidence when talking in front of many people and provides a method in improving all aspects of English.
